R:"Number of subsets of a set with \\(m\\) elements is \\(2^m\\)."
}

q {
Q:"If \\(f\\) is differentiable and \\(f(x)f'(x) < 0\\) for all real \\(x\\), then:"
A:"d"
O:a) "\\(f(x)\\) must be increasing", b) "\\(f(x)\\) must be decreasing", c) "\\(|f(x)|\\) must be increasing", d) "\\(|f(x)|\\) must be decreasing"
R:"If \\(f>0\\), \\(f'<0\\) (decreasing). If \\(f<0\\), \\(f'>0\\) (increasing towards 0). In both cases, magnitude \\(|f(x)|\\) decreases."
}

