R:"Repeated root \\(m=1/5\\). Solution \\(y=(c_1+c_2x)e^{x/5}\\). Conditions yield \\(c_1=1, c_2=1\\)."
}

q {
Q:"\\(P\\) is midpoint of chord from vertex of \\(y^2=8x\\) to another point. Locus of \\(P\\) is:"
