O:a) "\\(y^2=2x\\)", b) "\\(y^2=4x\\)", c) "\\(x^2/4+y^2=1\\)", d) "\\(x^2+y^2/4=1\\)"
R:"Let point be \\((x_1,y_1)\\). Midpoint \\((h,k) \\Rightarrow x_1=2h, y_1=2k\\). On parabola: \\((2k)^2=8(2h) \\Rightarrow k^2=4h\\)."
}

