q {
Q:"Eccentric angle in Q1 on \\(x^2/10+y^2/8=1\\) at distance 3 from center is:"
A:"b"
O:a) "\\(\\pi/6\\)", b) "\\(\\pi/4\\)", c) "\\(\\pi/3\\)", d) "\\(\\pi/2\\)"
R:"Point \\((\\sqrt{10}\\cos\\theta, \\sqrt{8}\\sin\\theta)\\). Distance sq: \\(10\\cos^2\\theta+8\\sin^2\\theta=9 \\Rightarrow 2\\cos^2\\theta=1 \\Rightarrow \\theta=\\pi/4\\)."
}

q {
Q:"Hyperbola transverse axis length \\(2a\\). Vertex bisects center-focus. Equation:"
A:"d"
O:a) "\\(6x^2-y^2=3a^2\\)", b) "\\(x^2-3y^2=3a^2\\)", c) "\\(x^2-6y^2=3a^2\\)", d) "\\(3x^2-y^2=3a^2\\)"
R:"\\(a = ae/2 \\Rightarrow e=2\\). \\(b^2 = a^2(e^2-1) = 3a^2\\). Eq: \\(x^2/a^2 - y^2/3a^2 = 1 \\Rightarrow 3x^2-y^2=3a^2\\)."
}

